{"tid":28940,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"搵工問題 求指點 酒水已準備","createTime":"2016-12-08T09:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T14:54:38.000Z","uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a691071a34991b07dbd26681131b3feaa6e7a12","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是咁的 <br />\n小妹十一月開始搵工 ，主要 admin /hr assistant 多。<br />\n前兩日開始狂apply ，前前後後二十幾份 ⋯ <br />\n但jobsDB status 話未睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好迷網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底有無策略 ？（聽人講零晨apply 好啲 ？）<br />\n或是有無其他app 搵 工 ？<br />\n<br />\nCv方面 ，都見過一兩次工 ，應該問題唔是出係CV到。 （好似係）<br />\n<br />\n最後一問 ， 巴絲們多數apply 咗幾耐先有call  ？ <br />\n心急搵工既FG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732d77c9ba1db9fbc0be082fd2eb46b9258f34cc","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"6789312b324f314b811cd1610cc3018e268f02b6","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"毒撚開post 無人應"},{"pid":"e71ac13be44c2292dc62784163fda03787391e30","tid":28940,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"失業真係好正 <br />\n<br />\n每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"a5cbf5ee98134e66f73dbc34f35411e62a9b79a2","tid":28940,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:09:15.000Z","msg":"hr問題可以去高登搵吉魯姐問下<br />\n佢多年專業經驗"},{"pid":"74236aa17ad5d3304194e7a9b88593a7039fae01","tid":28940,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"12月冇工搵都好正常<br />\n個個人等拎埋雙糧花紅唔肯走<br />\n冇人走邊有位請你<br />\n你等過埋農曆新年先搵工啦"},{"pid":"d41da05ad2fb51fe4bb585199d993f7eaa564301","tid":28940,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"唔關事，要見就會見你。<br />\n曾經做過聯絡，老闆試過收左成個月信先叫人黎；<br />\n亦試過今日收，聽日叫佢見。<br />\n<br />\n緣份也<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2822c6b9ff4a9ba1e1b901b5c6248543e309d266","tid":28940,"uid":21975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:21:41.000Z","msg":"唔覺零晨send CV有咩咁好<br />\n<br />\n如果你講到cv冇問題咁可能interview出問題<br />\n樓上巴打都岩，12月好淡，唔多工"},{"pid":"7e04ad2317a647daf52ac0d17460f7c990615ddb","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:35:07.000Z","msg":"好想番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43bd6d548541cc577abb1fb666ea6447aba235b","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hr問題可以去高登搵吉魯姐問下<br />\n佢多年專業經驗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明白 多謝巴打指點"},{"pid":"a3e1c27628cd33ca94cfcbffdf3e753e2d8e0e61","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺零晨send CV有咩咁好<br />\n<br />\n如果你講到cv冇問題咁可能interview出問題<br />\n樓上巴打都岩，12月好淡，唔多工</blockquo