開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人生無目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我目標就係唔駛返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bbe5fa7c8c329d38a2739b7448542fb4288f7c","tid":28940,"uid":29520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:01:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12月冇工搵都好正常<br />\n個個人等拎埋雙糧花紅唔肯走<br />\n冇人走邊有位請你<br />\n你等過埋農曆新年先搵工啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打講得岩呀 年尾個個都等攞bonus唔走<br />\n我都搵左3個月啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6390ccb98bca87c34d41fc8dac54965b98b86ec1","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>12月冇工搵都好正常<br />\n個個人等拎埋雙糧花紅唔肯走<br />\n冇人走邊有位請你<br />\n你等過埋農曆新年先搵工啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打講得岩呀 年尾個個都等攞bonus唔走<br />\n我都搵左3個月啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講多啲呀絲打 ，一齊分享吓。<br />\n我搵左一個月都係得中介介紹啲濕鳩工。<br />\n其實我做咩都冇太大所謂 ，文職萬呢蚊就心足。<br />\n但就係冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec9df0159be0d2fbfdda44400ffcde7b152af91","tid":28940,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:08:11.000Z","msg":"fg就去jijis搵工啦<br />\n<br />\n無特別就唔洗經jobsdb果d online apply<br />\n<br />\n正常send email就得,我就習慣早上10am send, 應該點都睇到呱<br />\n<br />\n公司真係要請人, 通常都會叫人in下先<br />\n<br />\n當年send完後4日內收到10個call interview"},{"pid":"3519662cc8b569e22df679e0f3962bc32fed50ff","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>fg就去jijis搵工啦<br />\n<br />\n無特別就唔洗經jobsdb果d online apply<br />\n<br />\n正常send email就得,我就習慣早上10am send, 應該點都睇到呱<br />\n<br />\n公司真係要請人, 通常都會叫人in下先<br />\n<br />\n當年send完後4日內收到10個call interview</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我來來去去都係收到啲中介call ⋯ <br />\n我都想interview <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔太驚interview 會出問題 ， 本身唔驚對人。<br />\n係sd 咗成個星期 ， 都無啲正正常常call <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開始擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f466e0350e021ddd6bde1a074500f9d969250b82","tid":28940,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:38:36.000Z","msg":"睇邊行，如果banking果啲back office admin野都可以係Efinancial開profile 搵/等人搵你.<br />\n想快就真係要搵唔同agent，Manpower, Adecco, Aston, PI Business, Cornerstone, etc.<br />\n<br />\n不過搵agent就記得問清楚係就個出糧，如果經agent出糧就唔好做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加油啦絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d734c3b17b64d6186c4d5946b8039ea56d98051","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇邊行，如果banking果啲back office admin野都可以係Efinancial開profile 搵/等人搵你.<br />\n想快就真係要搵唔同agent，Manpower, Adecco, Aston, PI Business, Cornerstone, etc.<br />\n<br />\n不過搵agent就記得問清楚係就個出糧，如果經agent出糧就唔好做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加油啦絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都知agent 會快 ，但好驚中伏。<br />\n其實我邊行無物所謂 ， 主要係想普普通通搵份文職做下等下年政府請文員。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知我好無大智嫁喇。不過jobsDB 好多sd 咗都唔睇/未睇 ，所以想上嚟問下有經驗嘅巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 