畫 ，又毒美劇。但都想有full time 經驗。咩都冇好難搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最衰身子差 ，唔係去考政府工就好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終極目標係同男朋友結婚 ，我就開畫廊教畫畫教鋼琴。但無本。所以現在咩工都想做。"},{"pid":"5a1dc9ade7d5efdc88cf44fbc79bf5ad7cf0e3ff","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你一樣10月尾11月頭揾工<br />\n都係無咩回音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然見完份，不過9成無offer</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇其他巴打講有得in 就有50%得。知唔知衰咩  ？得我學習下避免犯錯。"},{"pid":"5e19ee67a8e3a93a515190fc994b6f06a6e8a4ec","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"重有。好對唔住各位巴絲 ，開左post 先發現連登未有得賜酒。睇嚟要走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444fc1207cb7acaeb3ff506ee4ac12c092f68bc6","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:09:05.000Z","msg":"Btw 有冇人in 過 L.S. collection 嘅admin and hr assistant  ？ 有冇人可以比下意見點準備 ？ <br />\n除左化個妝著正齊呢啲門面野外 ，重有冇咩意見  ？ <br />\n<br />\n我驚我有盲目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝幫過小妹嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77480fea1b86f1e8655d41c88b709983df2f4275","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:09:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 有冇人in 過 L.S. collection 嘅admin and hr assistant  ？ 有冇人可以比下意見點準備 ？ <br />\n除左化個妝著正齊呢啲門面野外 ，重有冇咩意見  ？ <