03ffa4c7c6bae0d199f6b2840bb","tid":28940,"uid":9639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家年尾，個個等出完雙糧 bonus先走<br />\n加油啦，我舊年都好似你咁年尾點都揾唔到工<br />\n利申 15fg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後點？都係年頭先有人請？"},{"pid":"415b38b6f6c26d2a351461a2afa467ed21948eaa","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主咩學歷? 有INTERVIEW之前係咪唔會去查間公司?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我apply 之前會上網睇間公司資料 （新聞之類），到收到call 會再睇多次。但有啲公司就搵唔到太多資料。"},{"pid":"11664cf1b3b8722899b90785e79d1685305e4124","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依家年尾，個個等出完雙糧 bonus先走<br />\n加油啦，我舊年都好似你咁年尾點都揾唔到工<br />\n利申 15fg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後點？都係年頭先有人請？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過來人請指點 ⋯有巴打話話埋新年先搵 ，咁咪要再等多一兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n重點係唔想新年三姑六婆問起做咩唔識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3eda774c40d04c1b50001bfd5925513dbff446","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Btw 有冇人in 過 L.S. collection 嘅admin and hr assistant  ？ 有冇人可以比下意見點準備 ？ <br />\n除左化個妝著正齊呢啲門面野外 ，重有冇咩意見  ？ <br />\n<br />\n我驚我有盲<span style=\"color: red;\">點</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝幫過小妹嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\nno need to go</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁講嘅 ？"},{"pid":"2ccbc3fba8bebec341d4bf160bc6f11de1ac9d6e","tid":28940,"uid":1110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>依家年尾，個個等出完雙糧 bonus先走<br />\n加油啦，我舊年都好似你咁年尾點都揾唔到工<br />\n利申 15fg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後點？都係年頭先有人請？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過來人請指點 ⋯有巴打話話埋新年先搵 ，咁咪要再等多一兩個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n重點係唔想新年三姑六婆問起做咩唔識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我舊年直到三月先有offer，不過大公司黎，福利果d都唔錯。<br />\n年尾就比屋企人煩到頂唔撚順求其accept左某間大型時裝連鎖店做mt，實際係sales<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇你點睇，最緊要唔好比壓力自己。揾到份唔適合自己既，更加辛苦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2c32120ff41e398d4b04cb3856e3ed76bf5201","tid":28940,"uid":7332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T09:36:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Btw 有冇人in 過 L.S. collection 嘅admin and hr assistant  ？ 有冇人可以比下意見點準備 ？ <br />\n除左化個妝著正齊呢啲門面野外 ，重有冇咩意見  ？ <br />\n<br />\n我驚我有盲<span style=\"color: red;\">點</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝幫過小妹嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\nno need to go</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁講嘅 ？</blockquote><br />\n<em>我apply 之前會上網睇間公司資料 （新聞之類），到收到call 會再睇多次。但有啲公司就搵唔到太多資料。</em><br />\n睇睇"},{"pid":"a06ff8b083f43fbfb147848d3205c430e33f0089","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nno need to go</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解咁講嘅 ？</blockquote><br />\n&lt;em&gt;我apply 之前會上網睇間公司資料 （新聞之類），到收到call 會再睇多次。但有啲公司就搵唔到太多資料。&lt;/em&gt;<br />\n睇睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我再搵搵睇下其他資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2650077bd676bfa974e1208efa03d563c14026d","tid":28940,