多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你去interview 都比你睇下間公司既工作環境係點，比你感覺係咪舒服。我真係接受唔倒7日勞工假既公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心痴線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講多啲 ？ 咩野福利是正常 ？ <br />\n咩野都唔野驚比人壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553e60cc17ebeb419963e89b27f0edec3f330998","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3/4個offer <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都想做野。希望星期一interview 成功喇。雖然間公司好似話麻麻地。不過未有其他interview 只好頂硬上<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多公司都睇你language skills,英文普通話呢d,同埋睇你個人外唔外向，記住笑多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你去interview 都比你睇下間公司既工作環境係點，比你感覺係咪舒服。我真係接受唔倒7日勞工假既公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心痴線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講多啲 ？ 咩野福利是正常 ？ <br />\n咩野都唔識<span style=\"color: red;\">驚</span>比人壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c3e3c0bec54abbc345b52d72cd66348c460c9fe5","tid":28940,"uid":12788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多公司都睇你language skills,英文普通話呢d,同埋睇你個人外唔外向，記住笑多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋你去interview 都比你睇下間公司既工作環境係點，比你感覺係咪舒服。我真係接受唔倒7日勞工假既公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心痴線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講多啲 ？ 咩野福利是正常 ？ <br />\n咩野都唔識<span style=\"color: red;\">驚</span>比人壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我勤你唔好搵港資。港資真心唔好做，又孤寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出手又低<br />\n搵外資中資都唔好搵港資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n外資通常福利最好，我兩間公司都係外資，AL 起碼16-20日，有d港資會比7日你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常AL點都要12日 or up 啦&hellip;7日勞工假真係鬼也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7dded23dccd0fc50b4530ea6cef2035efbd780","tid":28940,"uid":43016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:46:33.000Z","msg":"hea埋個新年先"},{"pid":"c6cb5a10a9c129c67ef483d99f75ad144551ba5d","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以講多啲 ？ 咩野福利是正常 ？ <br />\n咩野都唔識<span style=\"color: red;\">驚</span>比人壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我勤你唔好搵港資。港資真心唔好做，又孤寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出手又低<br />\n搵外資中資都唔好搵港資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n外資通常福利最好，我兩間公司都係外資，AL 起碼16-20日，有d港資會比7日你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常AL點都要12日 or up 啦&hellip;7日勞工假真係鬼也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我都知好多港資好鳩 ，不過我真係有權簡咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFg 有權say no 咩。我真係好想番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然屋企唔等錢洗 ，不過我愈唔做野愈覺得自己廢。<br />\n想事但搵份工做住再轉工或草下experience。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想用哂所有錢回饋比父母 ，佢地供書教學咁多年 ，好想努力搵錢第一份薪水買份大禮比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愈咁諗就愈想搵到工 ，比佢地威比其他人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n覺得廢青係浪費青春同時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知我係港奴 ，但希望第一份工港奴搵到經驗就做番人唔做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再次多謝解答過我嘅巴絲 ，有你地我先覺得人生有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然聽日去in 間鳩鳩的公司 ，但希望就算失敗都可以搵啲interview 經驗令自己大膽啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n迷途羔羊上<br />\nSor for 1999"},{"pid":"669692e21f88bf868bf1c133d302735c5d9fd419","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hea埋個新年先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己比好大壓力自己 ，覺得每遲一日就浪費時間。<br />\n你都要加油好好享受人生。我係垃圾港奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385d6a6daf574aeda41ec786059b5a0763659670","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:00:56.000Z","msg":"講多啲 ，其實由細到大要物有物 ，身邊都係好人好朋友會幫我。我知職場險惡 ，好想鼓起勇氣邁出一步。投身社會唔再係溫室裏嘅小花。但又驚比人呃 ，所以真心好多謝幫過我嘅巴絲。迷惑中搵到人打救 ，有如雪中送炭。 謝謝各位巴絲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望聽日見工成功 ，唔成功都會再接再厲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aab34f6c0003bea7adddce9def1c97227789394","tid":28940,"uid":27220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"冇得急既.  第一份工作好重要. <br />\n我係9月graduate, 搵左3個月到搵到自己想做既公司.   JobsDB status doesn't matter la, the company will receive a email once you applied. They can read your CV without changing the status."},{"pid":"1fcc174e8ce1ce2bd128ef71ef60621bf09436fc","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇得急既.  第一份工作好重要. <br />\n我係9月graduate, 搵左3個月到搵到自己想做既公司.   JobsDB status doesn't matter la, the company will receive a email once you applied. They can read your CV without changing the status.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝謝你嘅意見。<br />\n<br />\n順便想問 ，剛in 完 ，好大機會得。因為對上兩個in 十多分鐘 ，我一in就in咗35-40分鐘。期間講咗好多公司架構等 ⋯<br />\n<br />\n重點係 ⋯ fg hr 11000會唔會太低定係咁上下 ？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd447c80056f49f0af2e3d5c1d3ca5be54436513","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:18:29.000Z","msg":"講多啲 ，係番5.5天長短週。<br />\n番工車程都要一個鐘多啲啲。剛入職咁計會唔會好低 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0428f3cc4a0410048d5a5a25ce35919839f71477","tid":28940,"uid":40775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講多啲 ，係番5.5天長短週。<br />\n番工車程都要一個鐘多啲啲。剛入職咁計會唔會好低 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返五日工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期六一來一回 其實已經冇左成日<br />\n<br />\n第一份工其實慢慢搵都未遲<br />\n我果陣fg鳩下鳩下 求其有份9k 都照做<br />\n諗返起都後悔"},{"pid":"85f56ce9fc76bee096fbb8974c435bb6b7191823","tid":28940,"uid":40775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:44:43.000Z","msg":"另外 福利方面<br />\n最多十日大假up<br />\n放銀行假<br />\n有醫療福利<br />\n有保險<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講"},{"pid":"11f2ac39a0cb6736354c06b8c831f091f69fb1e8","tid":28940,"uid":40775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外 福利方面<br />\n最<span style=\"color: red;\">好</span>十日大假up<br />\n放銀行假<br />\n有醫療福利<br />\n有保險<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講</blockquote>"},{"pid":"541620313d3757781de1762b7165aaf920cbd13c","tid":28940,"uid":12788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講多啲 ，係番5.5天長短週。<br />\n番工車程都要一個鐘多啲啲。剛入職咁計會唔會好低 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5.5 11k u grad ,叫佢食屎,正一垃圾公司，壓價壓成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nU grad 坐底最少13k ,唔好做壞手勢，下一份工係base on 你上一份工既salary 去adjust"},{"pid":"d760409edc343b89c9d8c786a99386ff004b01a3","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講多啲 ，係番5.5天長短週。<br />\n番工車程都要一個鐘多啲啲。剛入職咁計會唔會好低 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5.5 11k u grad ,叫佢食屎,正一垃圾公司，壓價壓成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nU grad 坐底最少13k ,唔好做壞手勢，下一份工係base on 你上一份工既salary 去adjust</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都係。不過我暫時重未有其他interview 或offer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗諗下 ⋯ 11k 做m記可能重高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f65cc989b9872c5747e84aeb264f40bc07f2d99","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外 福利方面<br />\n最多十日大假up<br />\n放銀行假<br />\n有醫療福利<br />\n有保險<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢無講福利 ，佢話 ⋯ 間間公司都無咁上下。<br />\n所以都唔知點再問落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74e811658a8825963222ad23ddb7ec90a44bd9de","tid":28940,"uid":46554,"li